  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Containing the spread of the COVID-19 epidemic and safeguarding livelihoods of vulnerable groups in slum areas</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To implement community based social interventions to decrease impact of the COVID19 and to prevent further spread of COVID-19 in particular vulnerable populations in slum areas in the capital Freetown through improved hygiene and access to safe community water supply combined with community awareness on preventive measures.


